Fun Facts about Venus Williams for Kids

Learn interesting trivia, information and fun facts about the American Tennis Player Venus Williams. Our facts files contain information about this successful African American professional tennis player who has been coached by her parents from a very young age; and played the game professionally since she was fourteen years of age. Check out our list of fun facts below which include the name of Venus' famous sister, the first tennis tournament she competed in, the name of her fashion design company and where she was born and raised. Learn, find and discover interesting information about this female tennis legend's lifetime including her most outstanding performances, the awards she has achieved and the records she holds.
